I would like to add another voice to JRA-1528, JRA-24374, JRA-14337, and I think even BAM-3101: I would like to be able to choose a notification scheme that is automatically assigned to new projects in place of "None."  It's easy to miss and then notifications don't work.

I understand that it could lead to notifications that aren't expected, but the user can choose to change the project to "None" at creation or in the future to avoid that - to my mind missing notifications when they're needed is a bigger danger than getting notifications when they aren't.

Thank you.

