In my company, we track items that are in the current sprint using a sprint fix version.  When a sprint is over, items that are unresolved often get moved into the following sprint.  I was excited to see the "WAS" operator in the latest major release of JIRA because I was hoping to be able to use it to get a snapshot of all the items that were in a prior sprint (fixVersion WAS "sprint 2").

Unfortunately the fixversion field is not supported by WAS, thus this ticket.

