Multiple web resource transformations chaining doesn't currently work.

Unfortunately, I don't think we have any guarantee over the ordering of the web transformations within the XML being preserved. It appears to be preserved on my small test of two web resource transformations - but there doesn't appear to be any promise made which would prevent the order from changing in the future.

Might need to introduce an order attribute for when we have more than one transformation applied to a web resource.

